Recommends: gnuradio
Description: GNU Radio source/sink blocks for bladeRF SDR hardware
 gr-bladeRF is a GNU Radio out-of-tree (OOT) module that provides
 source and sink blocks for the Nuand bladeRF software-defined radio
 family.
 .
 This package contains:
  * the gnuradio-bladeRF shared library,
  * PyBind11-based Python bindings,
  * GRC YAML block descriptions for GNU Radio Companion,
  * public C++ headers and the bladeRFConfig.cmake helper for
    building against the library.
